statement error
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX i_index ON s.test(LOWER(s))
----
is duplicated

statement ok
CREATE INDEX i_index ON s.test(LOWER(s))

query I
SELECT * FROM s.test WHERE LOWER(s)='hello'
